Category:Imperial Navy personnel of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: LT-514, born Obon Yandro, was a human male who, with the assistance of his AJ^6 cyborg construct, served as an Imperial controller within the Imperial Navy starfighter squadron Titan Squadron after the Battle of Endor. LT-514's quiet intelligence career was upturned after Endor. With the Empire needing field officers, he was thrilled to see the front lines. LT-514 served on the Imperial II-class Star Destroyer Overseer, commanded by Captain Terisa Kerrill.
